description:
Those star-shaped fasteners are everywhere on your bike, and you know one day you'll need a Torx wrench to tackle them. Bleed your brakes or replace bushings for your rear shock, you'll need the right tool for the job.

  • Made of shop-quality, high torque industrial steel
  • Convenient fold-up design
  • Multi-position composite handle is light, slip-resistant, and 40% stronger than steel
  • Includes T7, T9, T10, T15, T20, T25, T27, T30 and T40 wrenches
name: Park Tool TWS-2 Torx Compatible Wrench Set
